Directory for external libraries

* CIF Device Driver

Installation (Linux)
------------------------------------------------------------------------------
1. Download tarball from http://hilscher.com/download.htm , section Driver,
   File DRV-LNX (i.e. cifv2000.tgz). Unpack with tar -xvf cifv2000.tgz
2. Download and unzip the windows driver (see below) and move file DNM_USER.H
   to cif-V2.000/usr-inc/dnm_user.h
3. Go to cif-V2.000/api
4. Run make (to generate cif_api.o object)
5. Convert cif_user.h and dnm_user.h to UNIX format and apply patches:
   patch cif-V2.000/usr-inc/dnm_user.h dnm_user.h.diff 
   patch cif-V2.000/usr-inc/rcs_user.h rcs_user.h.diff 

Installation (Windows)
------------------------------------------------------------------------------
1. Download installation file from http://hilscher.com/download.htm , section
   Driver, File DRV-WIN (i.e. cif3111.zip)
2. Unzip with unzip cif3111.zip


* NI-DNET driver

Installation (Windows)
------------------------------------------------------------------------------
1. Download installation file from http://digital.ni.com/softlib.nsf/display?ReadForm&lookup=NI-DNET&view=current&node=132060_us
2. Start the installation

